( SNARLING )

21:25.910 --> 21:28.750
( MEOWING AND SNARLING )

21:56.480 --> 21:59.400
( APPLAUSE )

22:05.910 --> 22:07.870
( GROWLING AND SNARLING )

22:17.960 --> 22:19.510
( GROWLING )

